{"tid":854054,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"兔子拚命地拯救一隻被困住的貓! 感人！☺","createTime":"2018-10-09T05:34:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T06:40:10.000Z","uid":197098,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"abe02cdcb51a6b163ffd16a036fce97023a21616","tid":854054,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T05:34:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FydwwZtQyuiU&d=tpWi1nmtpTniQiL6rb93Dv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=2700bee3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">N.B.:</span> 實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>參觀然後領養</strong></span>，這裏有太多兔子需要一個家。詳情可去 <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=tpWi1nmtpTniQiL6rb93Dv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=836e2050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a>"},{"pid":"3cadbeb1bde5663eae9e242797c342f202c54bf8","tid":854054,"uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T06:09:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>兔仔在大自然的等級制度</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n在大自然內，兔仔有牠們的等級制度。一個高級(dominant)的兔仔會groom (舔和梳理) 一個次級(inferior)的兔仔。但高級的亦會要求次級的兔仔groom 牠，這是一定要服從的。當兔仔低頭向前躺在地上，牠就是想你groom (撫摸和親吻) 牠，這樣可以增加牠的自尊心、令牠舒適、快樂、心理健康。當牠們受驚時，也需要groom牠們，令牠們冷靜下來和知道是沒事的。兔子會騎着另一隻兔子背後來顯示牠是比較高層次的(show dominance), 這類行為停了就代表牠們已決定了等級制度。此行為是正常的，無論是雌性騎着雄性或兩隻同性別的騎着大家。<br />\n<br />\n兔仔是被捕獵的動物(prey animal)，在大自然內是每個捕獵者(predatory animal)的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，但牠們勝於速度, 跑得快。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚的。兔子喜歡吸引人注意，有時我們看電視的時候，兔子會躺在電視機前面，幸好牠們不知道我們其實不在看牠們。因此，經常陪牠們玩是重要的，兔子是群體性動物，如果主人沒有空，最好領養多一隻兔子陪伴牠。<br />\n<br />\n以下video是一個等級制度的例子, 可以在0:59 看到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Nyv4VhuZv_s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNyv4VhuZv_s&d=tpWi1nmtpTniQiL6rb93Dv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=2528685c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Nyv4VhuZv_s</a> <br />\n<br />\n如果你在兔兔面前打開手掌，對於牠來說是要求牠groom 你。如果主人和兔兔的關係好，牠會groom主人。如果牠對主人感到憤怒，對於牠來說，在牠面前打開手掌是不尊重牠，牠可能會用屁股對着你(代表生悶氣) 或嚴重的話，撲過來咬你。兔子憤怒的時候，耳朵會放在後面，耳口向側，姿勢站起來很硬對着你。(這個耳朵擺放姿勢同驚慌一樣，但驚慌時坐姿會蹲下。大家可以看我寫兔子驚慌的post) 以下video 是主人要求兔兔groom 主人的例子：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6DKeKyzZ67Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6DKeKyzZ67Y&d=tpWi1nmtpTniQiL6rb93Dv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=67cad871\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6DKeKyzZ67Y</a> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em>有趣video:</em></strong></span> 兩隻兔子正在決定等級制度，但遇到困難。兔子A groom 兔子B, 但groom 了很久和等了很久還未得到回報(兔子B groom A作為回報)，所以發脾氣在2:08咬兔子B。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/af7_mGuD5Qg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Faf7_mGuD5Qg&d=tpWi1nmtpTniQiL6rb93Dv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=0c60e2ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/af7_mGuD5Qg</a> <br />\n<br />\n除了騎着兔子背後，兔子還會躺在另一隻兔子的頸上來顯示牠是比較高層次的(show dominance), 這類行為停了就代表牠們已決定了等級制度:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/d9WUGogDlg4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fd9WUGogDlg4&d=tpWi1nmtpTniQiL6rb93Dv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=a8db2ea3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/d9WUGogDlg4</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">更多資訊：</span><a href=\"http://language.rabbitspeak.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flanguage.rabbitspeak.com%2F&d=tpWi1nmtpTniQiL6rb93Dv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=43f04d03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://language.rabbitspeak.com/</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://rabbit.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org%2F&d=tpWi1nmtpTniQiL6rb93Dv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=4dd07190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rabbit.org/</a>"},{"pid":"804c1cd966a47350ce0bbd1f51fa0f986822eec8","tid":854054,"uid":162316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T06:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213f98fc4c0b389240b8c607c50b79ffe6729590","tid":854054,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"804c1cd966a47350ce0bbd1f51fa0f986822eec8","tid":854054,"uid":162316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T06:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T06:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}